title: #ARTISTCEO: Dreams, Visions & Goals Accountability Check-In PART 2
desc: You attended the Nov. 14th workshop, did the exercises and are ready for more! You understand how important community is to achieving your dreams. Join a focused group of LA Artists and Creators who are committed to journeying together for 90 days, helping and supporting one another to achieve their goals and dreams. Everyone attending this workshop will report to the group on where they are with their SMART A goals, and where they need help. We will also brainstorm and share ideas around each person?s dreams, goals and action plan.? *Workshop Materials and Small Snack will be provided. *Parking on the Street
